'''安德魯·"安迪"·格芬'''（'''Andrew "Andy" Griffin'''，{{bd|1979年|3月7日|catidx=Griffin, Andy}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，擔任[[右後衛|右後衛]]。

==生平==
格芬的足球事業始於[[史篤城足球會|史篤城]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisisstaffordshire.co.uk/displayNode.jsp?nodeId=158315&command=displayContent&sourceNode=231466&home=yes&more_nodeId1=158332&contentPK=19521929 |title=STOKE CITY: I SHOULD NEVER HAVE LEFT, SAYS GRIFFIN |work=The Sentinel |date=2008-01-11 |accessdate=2008-01-11 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}{{en}}</ref></small>，其出色表現吸引了[[英超|英超]]球會[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]，在1998年1月格芬被紐卡素以150萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]簽下<small><ref name="bbc20040526">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/3749681.stm |title=Pompey swoop for Griffin |work=[[BBC|BBC]]體育 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2004-05-26 |accessdate=2008-01-11 |archive-date=2004-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040614184532/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/3749681.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

加盟[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]不久，格芬很快適應了球隊的戰術，亦入選了[[英格蘭U21|英格蘭U21]]國家隊<small><ref name="telegraph20021028">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml;jsessionid=T4JS1C0S5Y1I5QFIQMGCFFWAVCBQUIV0?xml=/sport/2002/10/28/sfnnew28.xml |work=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]] |publisher=Telegraph News and Media Limited |title=Griffin is amazed to discover hidden scoring touch |first=Rob |last=Stewart |date=2002-10-28 |accessdate=2007-08-12 }}{{Dead link}}{{en}}</ref></small>。

格芬在[[卜比·笠臣|卜比·笠臣]]的指導下頗受重用，2002/03年賽季的[[歐聯|歐聯]]對[[祖雲達斯|祖雲達斯]]的賽事更打進了一球<small><ref name="telegraph20021023">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/main.jhtml?xml=/sport/2002/10/24/sfgnew24.xml |work=[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]] |publisher=Telegraph News and Media Limited |title=Newcastle cut pride of Italy down to size |first=Henry |last=Winter |date=2002-10-23 |accessdate=2007-08-12 }}{{Dead link}}{{en}}</ref><ref name="guardian20021024">{{cite news |url=http://football.guardian.co.uk/Champions_League/Story/0,,817957,00.html |title=Griffin keeps Magpies alive |work=[[衛報|衛報]] |publisher=Guardian News and Media |first=Michael |last=Walker |date=2002-10-24 |accessdate=2008-01-12}}{{en}}</ref></small>。

由於在紐卡素的競爭激烈，2004年格芬[[博斯曼法案|免費轉會]]至[[樸茨茅夫足球會|樸茨茅夫]]。格芬共為紐卡素上陣97場，進3球<small><ref name="bbc20040526" /></small>。2006年夏天，[[哈利·列納|哈利·列納]]不把格芬納入球隊計劃，並打算把他外借至其他球會<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5396820.stm |title=Potters extend Griffin loan deal |date=2006-10-01 |accessdate=2008-01-11 |work=BBC體育 |publisher=BBC |archive-date=2016-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407154425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/5396820.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

格芬在2007年1月19日被外借返回母會[[史篤城足球會|史篤城]]至2007年6月，2006/07賽季末回到樸茨茅夫。期間格芬的表現令史篤城主教練[[東尼·佩利斯|東尼·佩利斯]]（Tony Pulis）希望把他簽下<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6683105.stm |work=BBC體育 |publisher=BBC |title=Stoke eye Hendrie & Griffin loans |accessdate=2007-05-23 |date=2007-05-23 |archive-date=2007-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071008191027/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6683105.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。2007年7月31日，格芬加盟[[打比郡足球會|打比郡]]，簽約3年<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/6925923.stm |work=BBC體育 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |title=Derby complete capture of Griffin |accessdate=2007-08-01 |date=2007-08-01}}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2008年1月11日，格芬再度回歸史篤城，轉會費30萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽下4年半合約<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7182290.stm|title=Griffin ties up Potters transfer|work=BBC體育|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2008-01-11|accessdate=2008-01-11}}{{en}}</ref></small>，穿上2號球衣。2008年1月31日，史篤城把[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[约翰·尤斯塔斯|伊斯泰斯]]（John Eustace）售往[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/watford/7220695.stm |work=BBC體育 |publisher=BBC |title=Stoke's Eustace moves to Watford |accessdate=2008-02-14 |date=2008-01-31 |archive-date=2008-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203200804/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/watford/7220695.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，格芬回歸僅三星期就成為球隊[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]<small><ref name="captain">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7225146.stm |work=BBC體育 |publisher=BBC |title=Griffin proud to be made captain |accessdate=2008-02-14 |date=2008-02-04 |archive-date=2008-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207164231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7225146.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，格芬認為這是職業生涯中最自豪的時刻<small><ref name="captain"/></small>。12月28日史篤城作客[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7788420.stm |title=West Ham 2-1 Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-28 |accessdate=2009-02-10 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7788420.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，下半場[[卡頓高爾|-{zh-hans:卡尔顿·科尔; zh-hk:卡頓·高爾;}-]]壓過格芬射入扳平，[[里卡多·弗勒|-{zh-hans:里卡多·弗勒; zh-hk:富拿;}-]]（Ricardo Fuller）不滿格芬犯錯而掌摑他，球證即時[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐富拿離場，史篤城在下半場大時間十人作戰而最終負1-2。

2010年1月12日只在季初於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]上陣3場的格芬獲外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]直到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5854321,00.html |title=Griffin completes Reading loan |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308035520/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5854321,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在為球隊上陣25場後，於7月1日以象徵費用正式加盟雷丁，簽約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/8779769.stm |title=Reading sign right-back Andy Griffin from Stoke City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-01 |accessdate=2010-07-02 |archive-date=2018-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830004922/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/reading/8779769.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

